  "description": "Synthetic monitoring: the Blackbox probes (internal app-health + external Cloudflare edge) and their alert signals.",
  "editable": false,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "id": null,
  "links": [],
  "liveNow": false,
  "panels": [
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "datasource",
        "uid": "grafana"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "code": {
          "language": "plaintext",
          "showLineNumbers": false,
          "showMiniMap": false
        },
        "content": "# Recollect — synthetic monitoring\nThe `blackbox` exporter's probes of the live service (`probe_success` 1=up/0=down, scraped by the on-box Prometheus). **Internal** probes (always on) hit the app over the compose network — *is the app up?*. **External** probes (opt-in; off until a domain is set) hit the public site + game through Cloudflare — *is it reachable from the outside?*. Internal-up + external-down ⇒ the edge/Tunnel/DNS, not the app. The **external panels are empty when external monitoring is off** (no domain ⇒ no series). Pages via the `synthetic-monitoring{,-external}` alert rules. See docs/observability.md §5.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "10.3.3",
      "title": "",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "description": "Current up/down of every probe (last sample). Internal: server-healthz / site-index / ws-origin. External: public-site / public-game (blank when external monitoring is off).",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "mappings": [
            {
              "options": {
                "0": {
                  "color": "red",
                  "index": 1,
                  "text": "DOWN"
                },
                "1": {
                  "color": "green",
                  "index": 0,
                  "text": "UP"
                }
              },
              "type": "value"
            }
          ],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": 1
              }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "short",
          "noValue": "no data"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 5,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 4
      },
      "id": 2,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "horizontal",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "textMode": "value_and_name"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "10.3.3",
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "probe_success",
          "instant": true,
          "legendFormat": "{{probe}}",
          "range": false,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Probe status (UP / DOWN)",
      "type": "stat"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "description": "Up/down history per probe across the dashboard window. Green = success (200 / TCP connect), red = failing. A red band on an external probe with the internal ones green localizes the fault to the edge/Tunnel/DNS.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "custom": {
            "fillOpacity": 80,
            "hideFrom": {
              "legend": false,
              "tooltip": false,
              "viz": false
            },
            "insertNulls": false,
            "lineWidth": 0,
            "spanNulls": false
          },
          "mappings": [
            {
              "options": {
                "0": {
                  "color": "red",
                  "index": 1,
                  "text": "DOWN"
                },
                "1": {
                  "color": "green",
                  "index": 0,
                  "text": "UP"
                }
              },
              "type": "value"
            }
          ],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": 1
              }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "short"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 9
      },
      "id": 3,
      "options": {
        "alignValue": "center",
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "showLegend": true
        },
        "mergeValues": true,
        "rowHeight": 0.9,
        "showValue": "never",
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "single",
          "sort": "none"
        }
      },
      "pluginVersion": "10.3.3",
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "probe_success",
          "legendFormat": "{{probe}}",
          "range": true,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Probe up/down timeline",
      "type": "state-timeline"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "description": "Probe round-trip duration per probe. External (https, through Cloudflare) is naturally slower than internal (compose-network); a sustained climb is an early degradation signal.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          },
          "custom": {
            "axisBorderShow": false,
            "axisCenteredZero": false,
            "axisColorMode": "text",
            "axisLabel": "",
            "axisPlacement": "auto",
            "barAlignment": 0,
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "gradientMode": "none",
            "hideFrom": {
              "legend": false,
              "tooltip": false,
              "viz": false
            },
            "insertNulls": false,
            "lineInterpolation": "linear",
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "pointSize": 5,
            "scaleDistribution": {
              "type": "linear"
            },
            "showPoints": "auto",
            "spanNulls": false,
            "stacking": {
              "group": "A",
              "mode": "none"
            },
            "thresholdsStyle": {
              "mode": "off"
            }
          },
          "mappings": [],
          "min": 0,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "s"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 17
      },
      "id": 4,
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "calcs": [
            "mean",
            "max"
          ],
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "showLegend": true
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "desc"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "probe_duration_seconds",
          "legendFormat": "{{probe}}",
          "range": true,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Probe latency (probe_duration_seconds)",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "description": "Uptime % per probe over the dashboard window (avg of probe_success). External probes show blank when external monitoring is off (no series).",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "mappings": [],
          "max": 100,
          "min": 0,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "yellow",
                "value": 99
              },
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": 99.9
              }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "percent",
          "noValue": "no data"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 17
      },
      "id": 5,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "horizontal",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "textMode": "value_and_name"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "10.3.3",
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "avg_over_time(probe_success[$__range]) * 100",
          "instant": true,
          "legendFormat": "{{probe}}",
          "range": false,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Uptime % (dashboard window)",
      "type": "stat"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "description": "Days until the earliest public TLS cert expires, per external HTTPS probe — (probe_ssl_earliest_cert_expiry - time()) / 86400. The recollect-probe-external-tls-expiry rule warns under 14 days. Empty when external monitoring is off (no HTTPS probe ⇒ no cert series). Cloudflare's edge cert normally auto-renews.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "mappings": [],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "yellow",
                "value": 14
              },
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": 30
              }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "d",
          "noValue": "external off / no cert"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 6,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 25
      },
      "id": 6,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "horizontal",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "textMode": "value_and_name"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "10.3.3",
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "(probe_ssl_earliest_cert_expiry{probe=~\"public-.*\"} - time()) / 86400",
          "instant": true,
          "legendFormat": "{{probe}}",
          "range": false,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Public TLS cert — days to expiry (external probes)",
      "type": "stat"
    }
  ],
